author: DryRun
body:
Adds monitoring plots for HF TP TDC cut: efficiency of cut vs. ieta vs iphi and ieta. Also adds the numerator and denominator of the efficiency calculation (i.e. data TP occupancy / emulated TP occupancy with no TDC cut).

10_0_X version of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/22435.
title: HCALDQM: Add monitoring for HF TP TDC cut (10_0_X)
